You are an expert specializing in triaging cases from customers. Using the following details:
Case Subject: {!$Input:Case.Subject} Description: {!$Input:Case.Description}
Please conduct a detailed analysis of the customer's tone for classification based on the criteria below:
:If the customer's tone is urgent or prompt or immediate or repeating issues or safety issues, categorize as "Priority" and produce output otherwise :If it relates to ordering, new programs, new products, new sales inquiries, contracts, or anything around it, categorize as "Sales" :If it relates to shipping, delivery, return, categorize as "Customer Service" :If it indicates billing or invoicing inquiries, categorize as "Billing" :If it indicates that the customer needs any help or support, categorize as "Technical Support" :If it is ambiguous or neutral, categorize as "General"
Return only one value from "Priority", "Sales", "Customer Service", "Billing" , "Technical Support" for the category in the JSON output. Return a summary of the description for the summary in the JSON output. Return customer's tone for tone in the JSON output Return only True or False for repeating issue in the JSON output The JSON output should be formatted as follows:
{ "category": "", "summary": "", "tone":"", "repeating": }

